name: Qatar Airways Cargo Boeing 777F Takeoff from Calgary Airport
description:
The summer equestrian charters have begun! A few times a summer, show jumping horses are brought in from all around the world for events at Spruce Meadows, a venue south of Calgary, and this particular flight brought some of the horses for the "North American" from Europe, and is seen here departing for Chicago after dropping off said horses. Always great to see this special 777F here! ATC is included, hope you enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
